strings.Value: "Those who don't wish to die for Irovetti may go. The others â€“ to arms!"
"So, the tyrant's henchmen! You're all guilty, and you will all die!"
"No one leaves here alive! I'll smash you against the walls!"

{n}It's noisy in the canteen: Irovetti's guards are vigorously discussing the ongoing battle.{/n} "The old families have started to riot. Street fights are springing up all over the city! We can't hold down the uproar! Irovetti's lost his grip, it's clear as day!"
"And that {Name}! Did you see {mf|him|her} handle Villamor? You think we stand a chance against {mf|him|her}? {mf|He|She}'s almost here! Let's run for it while we still can!"

{n}The wererat shows its crooked teeth in a fierce grin.{/n} "Cowardly, useless fools! Did you eat the royal food? Drink his wine? Stuff your pockets with his gold? Now you'll stay and fight for him! I'll eat the face of anyone who tries to escape!"
"{Name}! I will eat your liver! Gnaw out your guts! Suck the marrow from your bones!"
"Yes! Run, run! Ha ha ha! Hold on to your pants!" {n}Octavia smiles at you broadly.{/n}
